wwpLeosDnsClientMIB.name: wwpLeosDnsClientMIB

revisions.description: Add new MIB OIDs to support IP protocol version independent Inet addressing. New attributes include: wwpLeosDnsServerInetAddr, wwpLeosDnsServerInetAddrType.

wwpLeosDnsClientMIB.contactinfo: Mib Meister 115 North Sullivan Road Spokane Valley, WA 99037 USA Phone: +1 509 242 9000 Email: support@ciena.com
wwpLeosDnsClientMIB.description: A MIB module to manage dns client on the WWP products.

wwpLeosDnsClientStatus.name: wwpLeosDnsClientStatus
wwpLeosDnsClientStatus.description: Specifies whether or not the DNS client resolver is enabled or disabled.

wwpLeosDnsClientDhcpDomainName.name: wwpLeosDnsClientDhcpDomainName
wwpLeosDnsClientDhcpDomainName.description: Specifies the admin domain name configured by dhcp for this device.

wwpLeosDnsClientDhcpDomainNameState.name: wwpLeosDnsClientDhcpDomainNameState
wwpLeosDnsClientDhcpDomainNameState.description: Specifies if wwpLeosDnsClientDhcpDomainName is enabled or disabled.

wwpLeosDnsClientUserDomainName.name: wwpLeosDnsClientUserDomainName
wwpLeosDnsClientUserDomainName.description: Specifies the admin domain name configured by user for this device.

wwpLeosDnsClientUserDomainNameState.name: wwpLeosDnsClientUserDomainNameState
wwpLeosDnsClientUserDomainNameState.description: Specifies if wwpLeosDnsClientUserDomainName is enabled or disabled.

wwpLeosDnsServerTable.name: wwpLeosDnsServerTable
wwpLeosDnsServerTable.description: A table containing configured DNS Servers information. To create entry in this table use SNMP multiple set operation. Following mib objects must be set to create valid entry wwpLeosDnsServerAddr, wwpLeosDnsServerStatus

wwpLeosDnsServerEntry.name: wwpLeosDnsServerEntry
wwpLeosDnsServerEntry.description: Defines the information pertaining to a configured DNS Server.

wwpLeosDnsServerIndex.name: wwpLeosDnsServerIndex
wwpLeosDnsServerIndex.description: The unique index in DNS server table.

wwpLeosDnsServerAddr.name: wwpLeosDnsServerAddr
wwpLeosDnsServerAddr.description: The IP address for the configured DNS Server. wwpLeosDnsServerInetAddr cannot be set at the same time. This OID will be set to 0.0.0.0 when the server has an IPv6 address, which is shown in the wwpLeosDnsServerInetAddr and the wwpLeosDnsServerInetAddrType is set to ipv6. For a server with an IPv4 address, the ip address will be shown in this OID and the wwpLeosDnsServerInetAddr with the wwpLeosDnsServerInetAddrType set to ipv4.

wwpLeosDnsServerUserPriority.name: wwpLeosDnsServerUserPriority
wwpLeosDnsServerUserPriority.description: The priority of the dns server configured by user.

wwpLeosDnsServerDhcpPriority.name: wwpLeosDnsServerDhcpPriority
wwpLeosDnsServerDhcpPriority.description: The priority of the dns server configured by DHCP.

wwpLeosDnsServerScope.name: wwpLeosDnsServerScope
wwpLeosDnsServerScope.description: The object specifies the scope of this entry. Scope of the entry means who configured this entry. dhcp or user or both

wwpLeosDnsServerStatus.name: wwpLeosDnsServerStatus
wwpLeosDnsServerStatus.description: This object is used to create and delete rows in the wwpLeosDnsServerTable. To create a new row the management station must set the object to 'CreateAndGo'.

wwpLeosDnsServerInetAddrType.name: wwpLeosDnsServerInetAddrType
wwpLeosDnsServerInetAddrType.description: The Inet address type for the configured DNS Server. Used in conjunction with wwpLeosDnsServerInetAddr. When set to: ipv4 : wwpLeosDnsServerInetAddr should be compliant with InetAddressIPv4 from RFC 4001 ipv6 : wwpLeosDnsServerInetAddr should be compliant with InetAddressIPv6 from RFC 4001

wwpLeosDnsServerInetAddr.name: wwpLeosDnsServerInetAddr
wwpLeosDnsServerInetAddr.description: The Inet address for the configured DNS Server. This OID must be used in conjunction with wwpLeosDnsServerInetAddrType. The InetAddress specified here will be compliant with RFC 4001.

wwpLeosDnsServerExtTable.name: wwpLeosDnsServerExtTable
wwpLeosDnsServerExtTable.description: This table is an extension for wwpLeosDnsServerTable table. This table allows to set more attributes for DNS wwpLeosDnsServerTable table

wwpLeosDnsServerExtEntry.name: wwpLeosDnsServerExtEntry
wwpLeosDnsServerExtEntry.description: Defines the information pertaining to a configured DNS Server.

wwpLeosDnsServerAdminState.name: wwpLeosDnsServerAdminState
wwpLeosDnsServerAdminState.description: The object specifies the user admin state of this entry. User can configure this to enable | disable.

wwpLeosDnsServerOperState.name: wwpLeosDnsServerOperState
wwpLeosDnsServerOperState.description: The object specifies the operational state of this entry.

wwpLeosDnsServerEntryCompliance.name: wwpLeosDnsServerEntryCompliance
wwpLeosDnsServerEntryCompliance.description: The compliance statement of the wwpLeosDnsClient MIB.

wwpLeosDnsServerEntryIpv6Group.name: wwpLeosDnsServerEntryIpv6Group
wwpLeosDnsServerEntryIpv6Group.description: DNS server entry objects for IPv6 address.
